INSERT INTO event_log (
                event_id,
                event_type,
                schema_version,
                stream_key,
                occurred_at_epoch_millis,
                recorded_at_epoch_millis,
                attribution_character_id,
                source,
                payload_json
            )
            VALUES (?1, ?2, ?3, ?4, ?5, ?6, ?7, ?8, ?9)
            RETURNING global_seq
